{"tid":1940212,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"牛雜妹麵店食TG","createTime":"2020-03-23T15:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T06:16:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5a9a5a654aa044fab0d4e7b05130c7f6fc20d1","tid":1940212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/XDLWF42QSW36ZD2QWUPSSISIAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2FXDLWF42QSW36ZD2QWUPSSISIAY%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=696b2e3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2FXDLWF42QSW36ZD2QWUPSSISIAY%2F&h=3999df64\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/XDLWF42QSW36ZD2QWUPSSISIAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n牛雜妹麵店食TG<br />\n<br />\n「牛雜妹」李亦喬前日在社交網留言，表示前日警方為驅散在元朗紀念7.21恐襲八個月的市民而放催淚彈，令父母在元朗經營的粉麵店因未有提早關店，食正TG，她留言：「我舖頭中晒TG，我啲屋企人喺入面。」<br />\n<br />\n牛雜妹表示父母都在店中，她則在觀塘綵排，獲悉家人被困，她準備回店中了解情況，她前晚接受《蘋果》電話訪問時說：「收到朋友短訊通知先知道發生乜嘢事，亦聯絡店中父母，知道佢哋安全。爸媽話好彩唔喺我哋門口放，係喺對面舖，有一段距離，我哋關咗半閘，但啲催淚煙都吹到入眼，所以佢哋都出晒眼水。屋企人食到應一應，父母暫時留喺舖頭安全啲。」她表示慶幸當時店內食客已經離開。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：陳杰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200323/large/1584886367_6ba7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584886367_6ba7.jpg&h=ddc86c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛雜妹的父母在元朗經營食肆，前晚卻因警方放催淚彈而被困。互聯網圖片"},{"pid":"c1dff69cca14756d8ee45c6e6630f568b080ec1d","tid":1940212,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:12:43.000Z","msg":"其實佢好黃<br />\n<br />\n佢一早已經出聲"},{"pid":"e69f50979df7682229bf8be00f451034dcb7d6c0","tid":1940212,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"<a 